I used the code from the PathPlanner documentation for it, and I made sure I had my imports done. I did use Holonomic, and everything checks out. I asked Copilot, I asked the coding interface… Nothing helpful. The big one is that it keeps telling me to initialize the variable config outside of the try/catch, but if I do it gives a drive station error saying that it hasn’t selected an auto path.

It also doesn’t particularly help that PathPlanner keeps being weird with my autos and paths I make. It says they’re there, but I can’t find them in my code or on the dashboard…
